{
  "stem": "13469.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I should imagine there weren't very many Jewish shops in that area.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It just wasn't a very Jewish area of Berlin there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yes, we moved on then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In, in the beginning of 1936, there had been a lot of correspondence between my father and his brother in England-- Uncle Rudi, not to be confused with my brother, Rudi-- I better call him 'Ruti.' So, they had correspondence.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they came to the conclusion that we ought to go to London, and we ought to leave Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so in February 1936, my mother, Ruti, and me left Berlin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we traveled by train to Ostend, and then by boat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we arrived in London.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we stayed with this uncle and aunt, Rudi and Lotte in number 30, the avenue in northwest London in Willesden.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had a flat there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we stayed with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't have any children at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They'd only recently gotten married.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had both been lawyers-- or they'd had degrees in law from Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But, of course, they were not allowed to practice law because the law was different.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And anyway, it was a very restricted trade.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they were not allowed to practice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my father-- my Uncle Rudi, he got a job in the clothing trade-- rag trade in England and made his way from there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The interesting thing is that my father did not come with us to England.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that, in retrospect, of course, was a major mistake.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We have never been able to find out why he didn't come with us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It may be that he couldn't get a visa to come to England.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It may be that he couldn't get a work permit to come to England.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
